{"_path":"/maps/_devops/continuous-compliance","_dir":"_devops","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Continues Compliance 持续合规","description":"持续合规是一种跨领域的实践，旨在通过自动化和持续监控确保系统和流程始终符合相关法规和标准。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"brief"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Brief"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持续合规是一种实践方式，它通过自动化手段，持续确保软件开发过程和相关技术符合监管与安全标准。人工的合规检查不仅会拖慢开发进度，还容易引入人为错误；而自动化的检查和审计则可以提供更快速的反馈、更清晰的证据以及更简化的合规报告。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通过在持续交付（CD）流水线中集成策略即代码（policy‑as‑code）工具（例如 Open Policy Agent），并生成与 SLSA 指南对齐的软件物料清单（SBOM），团队可以在早期就发现并解决合规问题。将规则和最佳实践“代码化”，可以在不制造流程瓶颈的前提下，在各个团队之间一致地执行统一标准。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OSCAL 也显示出作为一个在大规模环境下自动化合规的框架的良好前景。目前，围绕持续合规的实践与工具已经足够成熟，理应被视为“理性的默认选项”，这也是我们将其推荐级别提升到“Adopt（采用）”的原因。随着 AI 在编码中的使用日益增加，以及人们对 AI 生成代码可能产生“盲目信任”和“懈怠”风险的担忧，将合规嵌入开发过程本身比以往任何时候都更加关键。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"来源：技术雷达"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"guide"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Guide"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_1-什么是持续合规continuous-compliance"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. 什么是“持续合规”（Continuous Compliance）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以这样向团队解释："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持续合规就是："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n不再把合规当成“上线前最后几周临时抱佛脚”的一次性活动，而是像自动化测试和持续集成一样，把合规则做成一条自动化的“生产线”，贯穿整个软件生命周期。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"关键要点："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持续性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：不是一年一次审计，而是每次提交代码、每次构建都自动检查。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自动化"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用工具和脚本代替人工勾勾画画的表格与文档。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"嵌入流程"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：合规检查内嵌在 CI/CD 流水线里，而不是额外的一道“闸门”。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_2-为什么要从人工合规升级到持续合规"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. 为什么要从“人工合规”升级到“持续合规”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以从三个角度来阐述："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"效率与交付速度"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人工逐条对照规范 → 审批周期长，拖慢发布。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自动合规检查 → 每次提交几分钟内给出结果，开发人员能快速修复。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"减少人为错误"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人看几十页规范，很容易漏项或理解偏差。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"规则代码化之后，每次检查执行的都是同一套逻辑，可重复、可追踪。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"审核与证据留存"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"监管或客户要求提供“你是如何达标的证据”时，自动化审计日志比 Word 文档更有说服力。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工具可以生成时间线：某次构建是否通过了哪些安全/合规规则，为什么失败，何时修复。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_3-持续合规的关键技术与实践"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3. 持续合规的关键技术与实践"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以按“实际落地要做什么”来拆分："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_31-策略即代码policy-as-code"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3.1 策略即代码（Policy as Code）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用类似 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Open Policy Agent（OPA）"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的工具，用策略语言（如 Rego）把合规规则写成代码。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"示例场景：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"限制哪些镜像仓库可以被使用；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"强制所有服务必须开启加密传输；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"禁止高危端口暴露在公网。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"好处："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"规则统一存放在代码库里，可版本控制、可 Code Review。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"规则变更可以像代码变更一样走流程，避免“口头规定”失真。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_32-在-cd-流水线中生成-sbom-并对齐-slsa"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3.2 在 CD 流水线中生成 SBOM 并对齐 SLSA"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SBOM（软件物料清单）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：类似“配料表”，列出软件中所有依赖组件、版本和来源。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 CI/CD 中自动生成 SBOM，并结合 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SLSA（Supply-chain Levels for Software Artifacts）"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的指导：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"明确每个构件的来源和构建过程是否可追溯；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"及早发现引入了存在漏洞或来源可疑的依赖。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这样可以："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"快速响应像 Log4Shell 这类供应链漏洞：一旦有新漏洞披露，可以立刻知道哪些服务受影响。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"满足越来越多法规对供应链安全透明度的要求。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_33-使用-oscal-实现大规模自动化合规"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3.3 使用 OSCAL 实现大规模自动化合规"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OSCAL（Open Security Controls Assessment Language）"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 是一种标准化格式，用来描述安全控制、评估结果和系统实现情况。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"价值在于：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把原本散落在文档里的合规要求结构化；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"让合规工具之间可以互通（不同系统都能读懂同一份 OSCAL 描述）。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对于大型组织或多云复杂环境，OSCAL 能帮助在多个系统之间统一描述与自动校验合规状态。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_4-adopt-的含义与为什么现在是默认选项"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4. “Adopt” 的含义与为什么现在是“默认选项”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在很多技术雷达或最佳实践指引中，"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“Adopt”"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 通常意味着："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这项技术或实践已经足够成熟；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"风险与成本可控；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"推荐大多数团队在没有特殊原因的情况下"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"优先采用"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，而不是“观望”。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把持续合规从“试验（Trial）/评估（Assess）”升级到“Adopt”，说明："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工具生态已经比较稳定（OPA、各种 SBOM 工具、OSCAL 生态等）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大量实践证明，持续合规可以：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"显著减少发布前的合规阻塞；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"降低审计成本；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提升安全与合规透明度。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与现有 DevOps / DevSecOps 流程的集成方式已相对清晰。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因此，现在更合理的思路是："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"默认做持续合规，只有在非常小的团队 / 非受监管业务下，才可以暂时不做或简化。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_5-在-ai-时代为什么把合规嵌入开发过程更关键"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5. 在 AI 时代，为什么“把合规嵌入开发过程”更关键"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 生成代码带来两类新的风险："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“看上去没问题”的代码实际上有隐患"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 可能引入不符合内部编码规范、安全控制或许可协议的代码（例如使用 GPL 代码片段）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开发者因为“生成很快”，反而降低了对细节的警惕。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"责任与可追踪性变得模糊"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"谁为 AI 生成的代码负责？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何证明某段代码在引入时通过了哪些合规/安全检查？"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把合规嵌入开发过程，可以通过："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在提交或合并请求阶段，自动扫描 AI 生成的代码是否：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用了不允许的第三方组件或许可证；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"违反安全编码规范；"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"没有满足数据处理与隐私条款（如访问日志未脱敏等）。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把检查结果与构建产物、提交记录绑定，形成可审计证据链。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这样，即便是 AI 生成的代码，也必须“通过同一套闸门”，避免因为“生成快”而“放松检查”。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"brief","depth":2,"text":"Brief"},{"id":"guide","depth":2,"text":"Guide","children":[{"id":"_1-什么是持续合规continuous-compliance","depth":3,"text":"1. 什么是“持续合规”（Continuous Compliance）"},{"id":"_2-为什么要从人工合规升级到持续合规","depth":3,"text":"2. 为什么要从“人工合规”升级到“持续合规”"},{"id":"_3-持续合规的关键技术与实践","depth":3,"text":"3. 持续合规的关键技术与实践"},{"id":"_4-adopt-的含义与为什么现在是默认选项","depth":3,"text":"4. “Adopt” 的含义与为什么现在是“默认选项”"},{"id":"_5-在-ai-时代为什么把合规嵌入开发过程更关键","depth":3,"text":"5. 在 AI 时代，为什么“把合规嵌入开发过程”更关键"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_devops:continuous-compliance.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_devops/continuous-compliance.md","_stem":"6.maps/_devops/continuous-compliance","_extension":"md"}